Lagarde Says IMF Will Do All It Can to Help Europe Fight Crisis

-- B y   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i
-- 
2011-10-21T11:58:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/lagarde-says-imf-will-do-all-it-can-to-help-europe-fight-crisis.html
International Monetary Fund
Managing Director  Christine Lagarde  said the fund will do all it
can to help the European Union solve its debt crisis. She spoke
to reporters in Brussels today before a meeting of euro area
finance ministers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Vasarri in Brussels at 
